title: [PIP-8] Incentivizing Pickle Holding and Governance Reform
body:
A proposal by the Pickle Core Devs.

This proposal addresses the concerns regarding the lack of an intrinsic reason to hold PICKLEs, the need for a more democratic governance structure, and the drawbacks of a buy and burn strategy for the PickleJars.

If this proposal is passed, the following steps will be taken:

1. Allow staking of PICKLEs to earn a portion of PickleJar profits
2. Roadmap towards a community-controlled treasury
3. Send the bulk of PickleJar fees to the treasury

The details of how this proposal will be implemented can be found here on the forum: https://forum.pickle.finance/t/rfc-incentivizing-pickle-holding-and-governance-reform/182

It is highly encouraged that you read the initial post before voting.
